## Architecture & Patterns

- **Two app modes** — `App.jsx` switches between **Interactive Demo** (sidebar-navigated) and **Customer Journeys** (step-by-step walkthroughs). State lives in `AppContext`.
- **No router library** — view navigation is state-driven via `AppContext.navigateTo(viewId)`
- **Data layer** — `src/data/databricksData.js` makes real API calls to the FastAPI backend; `mockData.js` is the fallback
- **Slot pattern** — `LeadDetail` accepts slot props for composing enrichment forms, contact buttons, etc.
- **Dashboard pattern** — "This Week" snapshot cards + "4-Week Trend" MiniBarChart grids

## Commands

```bash
npm run dev      # Start Vite dev server (frontend only)
npm run build    # Production build (run before deploying)
npm run preview  # Preview production build
npm run lint     # ESLint
```

